divs: Sighting Detailsi don't know what comets look like i have never actually seen one in real life but i have seen videos and photos of them when they usually fly across the sky they leave a trail behind them well this object that i saw last night didn't have a trail behind it and it flew across the sky very fast the sighting lasted only about three seconds i thought i would post it because it could have possibly been a ufo it didn't look like a comet but it had similarities
Summary: well it looked like a snowball maybe ufo or comet?
